alpha.com/symbol/IVOL#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"Quadratic Interest Rate Volatility and Inflation Hedge ETF New\">IVOL</a>) is an exchange-traded fund that we have covered in the past. We have a few articles out on the name, the first one related</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1320226467/image_1320226467.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742730-ivol-abandoning-ship-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 06:47:00"}, {"id": "4742729", "title": "CEF Weekly Review: BlackRock Doubles Down On Distribution Strategy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119762876/image_119762876.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"IMG_1955.jpg\" data-id=\"119762876\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119762876/image_119762876.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119762876/image_119762876.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119762876/image_119762876.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119762876/image_119762876.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119762876/image_119762876.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119762876/image_119762876.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119762876/image_119762876.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119762876/image_119762876.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Vincent Besnault</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Welcome to another installment of our CEF Market Weekly Review, where we discuss closed-end fund (\"CEF\") market activity from both the bottom-up \u2013 highlighting individual fund news and events \u2013 as well as the top-down \u2013 providing an overview of the broader market. We also try to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/119762876/image_119762876.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742729-cef-weekly-review-blackrock-doubles-down-on-distribution-strategy", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 06:32:00"}, {"id": "4742728", "title": "Wayfair: Increased Spending Lowers Its Q4 2024 Adjusted EBITDA Outlook", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170420513/image_2170420513.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wayfair Store\" data-id=\"2170420513\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170420513/image_2170420513.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170420513/image_2170420513.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170420513/image_2170420513.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170420513/image_2170420513.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170420513/image_2170420513.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170420513/image_2170420513.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170420513/image_2170420513.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170420513/image_2170420513.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">patty_c</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Wayfair's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/W\" title=\"Wayfair Inc.\">W</a></span>) <a href=\"https://investor.wayfair.com/news/news-details/2024/Wayfair-Announces-Third-Quarter-2024-Results-Reports-Strong-Profitability-in-Tandem-with-Further-Market-Share-Gains/default.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">Q3 2024 results</a> were largely in-line with expectations, but its <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4234417-wayfair-wipes-out-early-gains-cautious-outlook-for-q4\">guidance for Q4 2024</a> indicated plans for higher spending and consequently lower adjusted EBITDA margins. Wayfair expects 2% to 4% adjusted EBITDA margins in Q4 2024</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170420513/image_2170420513.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742728-wayfair-increased-spending-lowers-its-q4-2024-adjusted-ebitda-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 06:17:25"}, {"id": "4742734", "title": "Fixed-Income Outlook: A New Environment For Bonds", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Fixed income concept. Types of investment security that pay investors fixed interest or dividend payments until their maturity date. Finance business conceptual. Money bag.\" data-id=\"1625101509\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"910px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Andrii Yalanskyi</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Gene Tannuzzo, CFA</em></p> <p></p> <h2>Transcript</h2> <p><strong>Gene Tannuzzo, CFA, Global Head of Fixed Income -</strong> I think the biggest transition that occurred in 2024 is that the Fed moved from being on hold with tight monetary policy to reducing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1625101509/image_1625101509.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742734-fixed-income-outlook-new-environment-for-bonds", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 06:10:00"}, {"id": "4742731", "title": "Income Investing Playbook 2025: Ideas For A New Rate Cycle", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Coin graph with percentage signs on top\" data-id=\"2158301114\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <blockquote><p>Higher long-term yields and a normalizing yield curve may signal new opportunities for income investors in 2025, even as rate cuts and economic uncertainty shape the market.</p></blockquote> <h2>Introduction to Income Investing</h2> <p>Income investing is a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301114/image_2158301114.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742731-income-investing-playbook-2025-ideas-new-rate-cycle", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 05:45:00"}, {"id": "4742724", "title": "Bausch + Lomb And Bausch Health: Some Incremental Progress As We Wait For Sale News", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man trapped in the middle of a sea of sharks on chair\" data-id=\"108311069\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">mrPliskin/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Overview</h2> <p>As I noted in my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4722174-sale-rumors-lift-both-bausch-and-lomb-parent-bausch-health-breakthrough-likely\">last update</a> on <b>Bausch + Lomb Corporation </b>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BLCO\" title=\"Bausch + Lomb Corporation\">BLCO</a></span>) and <strong>Bausch Health Companies Inc.</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BHC\" title=\"Bausch Health Companies Inc.\">BHC</a></span>) in September, in which I gave \u201cBuy\u201d ratings to both, the two companies' fates</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/108311069/image_108311069.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742724-bausch-plus-lomb-and-bausch-health-some-incremental-progress-as-we-wait-for-sale-news", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 03:30:16"}, {"id": "4742723", "title": "Cardlytics Continues Revenue Contraction Amid Worsening Economics", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesses use smartphones with online banking digital technology, mobile banking for shopping, payment, finance, bank, account, transfer, credit card, financial and global business online\" data-id=\"2143222197\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2143222197/image_2143222197.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/214322219